### 6. UI Component Selection (Frontend Apps)

**Ambiguous Prompt Patterns:**
- "ticket sidebar with button"
- "UI to configure settings"
- "show results to user"
- No specific UI components mentioned

**Decision Tree:**

```
What does the UI need to do?
├─ TRIGGER ACTION (create, send, export)
│   Component: fw-button
│   Example: <fw-button color="primary">Create Issue</fw-button>
│   Add: Loading state (fw-spinner), success/error message (fw-inline-message)
│
├─ DISPLAY STATUS (show sync status, connection state)
│   Components: fw-label + fw-inline-message
│   Example: 
│     <fw-label value="Sync Status"></fw-label>
│     <fw-inline-message type="success">Synced 5 minutes ago</fw-inline-message>
│
├─ COLLECT INPUT (select options, enter text)
│   Components:
│   ├─ Dropdown: fw-select with fw-select-option
│   ├─ Text: fw-input
│   ├─ Multi-line: fw-textarea
│   ├─ Checkbox: fw-checkbox
│   └─ Radio: fw-radio-group with fw-radio
│
├─ SHOW RESULTS (display data, list items)
│   Components: fw-data-table or custom HTML with fw-label
│   Example:
│     <fw-label value="Created Items"></fw-label>
│     <div class="results-list">...</div>
│
└─ CONFIRM ACTION (are you sure?)
    Component: fw-modal with fw-modal-title, fw-modal-content, fw-modal-footer
    Example: Show modal before destructive action
```

**Standard UI Pattern for Action Apps:**

```html
<!-- Ticket sidebar for creating external items -->
<div class="app-container">
  <!-- Header -->
  <fw-label value="Create External Item"></fw-label>
  
  <!-- Configuration (if needed) -->
  <fw-select id="targetSelect" label="Select Target" placeholder="Choose...">
    <fw-select-option value="1">Option 1</fw-select-option>
  </fw-select>
  
  <!-- Action Button -->
  <fw-button id="createBtn" color="primary">Create Item</fw-button>
  
  <!-- Loading State (hidden by default) -->
  <fw-spinner id="loadingSpinner" size="small" style="display: none;"></fw-spinner>
  
  <!-- Result Message (hidden by default) -->
  <fw-inline-message id="resultMsg" type="success" style="display: none;">
    Item created successfully!
  </fw-inline-message>
  
  <!-- Result Link (if applicable) -->
  <div id="resultLink" style="display: none;">
    <fw-label value="View Item"></fw-label>
    <a id="itemUrl" href="#" target="_blank">Open in new tab</a>
  </div>
</div>
```

**Decision Rule:**
```
If prompt says "ticket sidebar" or "UI":
  1. Determine primary action (create, export, sync, view)
  2. Use standard UI pattern above
  3. Always include: button, loading state, success/error message
  4. Add result link if creating external item
  5. Use Crayons components ONLY (no plain HTML buttons/inputs)
```

